{"tid":1527942,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[罷鐵] 塞鐵不如全民跳閘","createTime":"2019-09-01T12:00:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T12:14:11.000Z","uid":263839,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3b6c02893c7ed894aa0c62e9b15290daf93dd787","tid":1527942,"uid":263839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:00:36.000Z","msg":"見到telegram有手足籌備緊罷鐵<br />\n係度想講比少少忠告大家<br />\n<br />\n之前罷鐵比外人屌係因為阻住佢地番工番學<br />\n因為你地的確係阻撚住晒 係外人觀感一定唔會好<br />\n雖則外人點睇唔重要 因為你地已經唔記得左<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不合作港鐵而唔係不合作市民!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n參考番早前手足<span style=\"color: red;\">紅隧唔收錢比車過去不合作政府</span><br />\n適逢大家都可能<span style=\"color: red;\">未有心理準備跳閘</span><br />\n希望手足唔好幫<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">大家全民跳閘</span></span>!!<br />\n<br />\n出入閘比錢即係送錢比佢地<br />\n我地唔好不合作, 應該要送錢比佢地!<br />\n<br />\n如果大家係<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全港任何地鐵站幫市民唔使比錢就入閘</span></span><br />\n詳細做法例如<br />\n打開地鐵入閘道職員入口<br />\n搵手足夾硬拆左入閘舊野等等<br />\n港鐵會賺少好多架!!<br />\n<br />\n打工仔們見到你免費比佢搭地鐵又唔會屌你<br />\n由得你地不合作港鐵<br />\n咁香港一定會亂架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔想香港亂....<br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df93760de8f55ea2f6f5834d8d8e8c8235023a2b","tid":1527942,"uid":263839,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:00:57.000Z","msg":"唔想睇到香港再亂啦..."},{"pid":"58dbc4861d8155b4c7295b56de65df69542a2cbb","tid":1527942,"uid":263839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:01:35.000Z","msg":"求下大家合作少少..."},{"pid":"236ec1ef9539ba3934b1a278f753676a7bcc19e5","tid":1527942,"uid":292868,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"df93760de